%N A016039 Inverse of 2030th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A016039 Periodic with period length 2030. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A016039 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A016039/b016039.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000</a>
%H A016039 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 2030.
%H A016039 <a href="/index/Rec#order_672">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 672.
%H A016039 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A016039 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%o A016039 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(2030)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
